				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">A 16 KiB PRG ROM such as Duck Hunt or Donkey Kong is loaded into both $8000 and $C000. What happens at the hardware level is <a href="http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/Mirroring" class="postlink">mirroring</a>: the PRG ROM is ignoring A14 when deciding which byte to output.</div>

