				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">For the same reason that a value written to $0123 isn't considered &quot;copied&quot; to $0923, $1123, and $1923. The same RAM just appears four times in the memory map. Likewise, a 16 KiB PRG ROM appears twice in the memory map unless it uses CPU A14 as an additional positive enable (which it doesn't).</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

